  {
    icon: '🕒',
    title: 'Covers Your Survey-Day Email Gap',
    text: "Damp surveyors spend entire days inside properties — in cellars, sub-floor voids, and lofts. A solicitor's email arriving at 9:30am sits unopened until late afternoon. The sixty-second acknowledgement ensures your company responds faster than every competing PCA firm."
